# Split - Configurações (RT1-St / SW1-St)

## Parte 2 - Clear Configs and reload equipment (Router e Switch)

### Router(RT1-St)
enable
erase startup-config (enter)
reload (no save)

### Switch(Sw1-St)  
enable
erase startup-config (enter)
delete flash:vlan.dat (enter enter)
reload (no save)

- check SDM
enable
show sdm prefer

- if necessary 
configure terminal
sdm prefer dual-ipv4-and-ipv6
end
copy running-config startup-config
reload

## Parte 3 -  Perform Equipment Initial Configuration (Router e Switch)

### Router (RT1-St)

enable
configure terminal
no ip domain-lookup
hostname RT1-St
ip domain-name isepacademy.ccna.itn.com
security passwords min-length 10
service password-encryption
enable secret classclass
username cisco privilege 15 secret classclass
crypto key generate rsa modulus 1024
ip ssh version 2
line console 0
 password classclass
 login
exit
line vty 0 15
 exec-timeout 0 30
 login local
 transport input ssh
exit
login block-for 300 attempts 3 within 120
banner motd #
AVISO: Acesso restrito a pessoal autorizado.
Todas as tentativas de acesso sao registadas e monitorizadas.
#
ip host RT1-Zg 172.20.7.97
ip host RT1-Pl 10.0.0.2
ip host RT1-St 10.0.0.6
ip host MLS1-Zg 172.20.7.98
ip host MLS2-Zg 172.20.7.102
ip host SW1-Zg 172.20.7.4
ip host SW2-Zg 172.20.7.5
ip host SW1-Pl 172.20.11.106
ip host SW1-St 172.20.13.234
end
